Title: Baling Supports the Moon
---
\[Yuanwu's] Appended pointer says：

A test is raised to examine it：

Raised：

A monk asked Baling. "So what is the 'Blown Hair
Sword'?"

Ling said. "Branch by branch, the coral is supporting
the moon."
